hmmm.. well yesterday.. i woke up at megans at 10.. i went home and watched tv till noon then i slept noon to three then i got up and at 430 i went with my mom to get my check. then she made me go to the barn with her.. then we went grocery shopping. we got home around 730 then we ate supper. hmm then i went to megans til 10 and then i came home and pretty much went to bed cuz there is nothing to do at my moms. then this morning i woke up and watched tv.. then my dad showed up at my house at 1230ish and i went with him now i am here sitting. i added new pictures to my myspace. so you should comment them. yeah well ill write soon.

nothing new really.. umm i guess ill tell you about my week from thursday til now.. umm thursday i babysat.. pretty much it.. friday.. i went out to eat to los banditos.. man do i love that place! then i slept over at megans! man that was grand. saturday morning i had to work.. then i hung out with megan and leah and courtney.. then leah slept over at my house saturday night.. hmm.. then sunday.. we woke up and went to megans for like an hour.. then me and leah walked to leahs house.. then my mom called me there and said that i was suposta be at work.. so i ended up being an hour late.. :( that sucked. leah has these freakin adorable 2 week old puppies.. i want one horribly! hmm.. when i got done with work at 2.. i went to megans again.. and courtney was just leaving.. then my dad got done with work at 4 so he picked me up on his way home.. and then today.. my dad called this ask-a-nurse thing.. cuz he has no feeling in two of his fingers.. he doesnt know what it is.. and then he told me the nurse said it might be signs of a stroke.. and his blood pressure is really high.. then his friend called and i was listening in cuz they were talking about it all.. and they all think that it might be signs too.. so im really scared.. i went down by him when he got off the phone cuz i was crying.. and idk what i would do without him.. :'( but hes going to the doctor friday.. i hope hes okay.. but anyways.. i think i'm hanging out with alicia.. but im not sure.. well i guess i'll write later.
